Class RDFConnectionModular

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.rdfconnection.RDFConnectionModular
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, RDFConnection, RDFDatasetAccessConnection, RDFDatasetConnection, SparqlQueryConnection, SparqlUpdateConnection, Transactional

    public class RDFConnectionModular
extends Object
implements RDFConnection
    Implementation of RDFConnection where the query, update and graph store operations are given by specific implementations of the respective interfaces.
